https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kBV7IgBXzfOEa7WO908HkAwFEYz.jpg Journey to Luckenbach, Texas, the place "where everybody's somebody." The documentary film Back to the Basics traces the history of Luckenbach from a one horse crossroads to its iconic status as a cultural mecca with its unique country flavor and distinct musical legacy.
